headDescription: FETISHGROUND is a electronic music project by ONE 0000 0001
pageHeaderImageAlt: Fleshware with a gasmask for the header image
sectionTextP: I started composing for this project in 2007 as Fleshware. It took me years to create the seventeen tracks of my debut album 'A la recherche de soi-même...'. I qualify this album as Oppressiv Elektro Pop.
After this album, I made some more experimental ambiant EPs.
I, as ONE 0000 0001, currently rework or make a video for each track of the album 'A la recherche de soi-même...'.

sectionCardData: The first EP released in march 2014 on bandcamp. This is the most experimental.
The second EP released in july 2014 on bandcamp after the debut album. It's a dark experimental ambiant EP.
The third EP released in february 2015 on bandcamp. It's a experimental atmospheric ambiant EP.
